{"tid":2194631,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"搭咗農夫山泉架沉船嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-09-08T15:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T01:53:40.000Z","uid":150100,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70828225ea67cc603fa809e2799cb7ccef4886c4","tid":2194631,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"我與你同坐這沉船，無情浪把它猛捲<br />\n滿天風雨，四十未能見，亂作一大團，不知怎算。<br />\n既決意留在這沉船，齊齊令它不遭破損<br />\n困境挑戰，奮勇地面對，令到這條船，永不翻轉。<br />\n<br />\n山頂是我家，一手五廿三，實在極不願，低位賤賣做二等股民<br />\n破鏡明日定會重圓，時局定必得好轉，懷著希冀，<br />\n再創造時勢，令到這條船，永久溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n山頂是我家，怎捨得沽了它，實在極不願，低位賤賣做韭菜斟茶，<br />\n緊緊抱著tesla，傾出這心裏話，但藉著這番話，齊齊共你發洩一下，<br />\n但願日後ifc下，人人賺錢，永不分化。"},{"pid":"9cd5e257e385e61955364e409182d40a91466b23","tid":2194631,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba94df2d6873162e3d3ec72e6f938f64201a28e","tid":2194631,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf8d28243d7d7444cf4dc5075fe583e33492639","tid":2194631,"uid":219244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tan74Uy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftan74Uy.gif&h=363a475c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da432c61f8f9ce6b9acb7eeb9e14da8b5df4aee0","tid":2194631,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf8d28243d7d7444cf4dc5075fe583e33492639","tid":2194631,"uid":219244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tan74Uy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c